{"translation-revision-date":"2026-07-02 03:53:52+0000","generator":"GlotPress\/4.0.3","domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","plural-forms":"nplurals=3; plural=(n == 1) ? 0 : ((n >= 2 && n <= 4) ? 1 : 2);","lang":"sk"},"Font family to uninstall is not defined.":["Nie je definovan\u00e1 rodina p\u00edsma na odin\u0161talovanie."],"paging\u0004<div>Page<\/div>%1$s<div>of %2$d<\/div>":["<div>Strana<\/div>%1$s<div>z %2$d<\/div>"],"noun\u0004Upload":["Nahra\u0165"],"variation label\u0004%1$s (%2$s)":["%1$s (%2$s)"],"There was an error updating the font family. %s":["Pri aktualiz\u00e1cii rodiny p\u00edsma do\u0161lo k chybe. %s"],"font source\u0004Custom":["Vlastn\u00fd"],"font source\u0004Theme":["Z t\u00e9my"],"Font family updated successfully.":["Rodina p\u00edsma bola \u00faspe\u0161ne aktualizovan\u00e1."],"Lowercase letter A\u0004a":["a"],"Uppercase letter A\u0004A":["A"],"Font library\u0004Library":["Kni\u017enica"],"There was an error installing fonts.":["Pri in\u0161tal\u00e1cii typov p\u00edsma do\u0161lo k chybe."],"font categories\u0004All":["V\u0161etky"],"Current page":["Aktu\u00e1lna str\u00e1nka"],"No fonts installed.":["Nie s\u00fa nain\u0161talovan\u00e9 \u017eiadne typy p\u00edsma."],"Connect to Google Fonts":["Pripoji\u0165 ku Google Fonts"],"Revoke access to Google Fonts":["Zru\u0161i\u0165 pr\u00edstup ku Google Fonts"],"No fonts found to install.":["Nena\u0161li sa \u017eiadne p\u00edsma na in\u0161tal\u00e1ciu."],"Error installing the fonts, could not be downloaded.":["Pri in\u0161tal\u00e1cii p\u00edsiem sa vyskytla chyba, nepodarilo sa ich stiahnu\u0165."],"Uploaded fonts appear in your library and can be used in your theme. Supported formats: .ttf, .otf, .woff, and .woff2.":["Nahran\u00e9 typy p\u00edsma sa zobrazia vo va\u0161ej kni\u017enici a mo\u017eno ich pou\u017ei\u0165 vo va\u0161ej t\u00e9me. Podporovan\u00e9 form\u00e1ty: .ttf, .otf, .woff, and .woff2."],"Are you sure you want to delete \"%s\" font and all its variants and assets?":["Naozaj chcete odstr\u00e1ni\u0165 typ p\u00edsma \"%s\" a v\u0161etky jeho varianty a zdroje?"],"There was an error uninstalling the font family.":["Pri odin\u0161talovan\u00ed rodiny p\u00edsma do\u0161lo k chybe."],"%d variant":["%d variant","%d varianty","%d variantov"],"font style\u0004Normal":["Norm\u00e1lny"],"font weight\u0004Normal":["Norm\u00e1lna"],"Library":["Kni\u017enica"],"font weight\u0004Semi-bold":["Polotu\u010dn\u00e9"],"font weight\u0004Extra-bold":["Extra tu\u010dn\u00e9"],"font weight\u0004Extra-light":["Extra tenk\u00e9"],"Font name\u2026":["N\u00e1zov p\u00edsma..."],"Upload font":["Nahra\u0165 p\u00edsmo"],"Allow access to Google Fonts":["Povoli\u0165 pr\u00edstup ku Google Fonts"],"Select font variants to install.":["Vyberte varianty fontu na in\u0161tal\u00e1ciu."],"Fonts":["Typy p\u00edsma"],"Install Fonts":["In\u0161talova\u0165 typy p\u00edsma"],"Fonts were installed successfully.":["Typy p\u00edsma boli \u00faspe\u0161ne nain\u0161talovan\u00e9."],"To install fonts from Google you must give permission to connect directly to Google servers. The fonts you install will be downloaded from Google and stored on your site. Your site will then use these locally-hosted fonts.":["Ak chcete nain\u0161talova\u0165 typy p\u00edsma od spolo\u010dnosti Google, mus\u00edte udeli\u0165 povolenie na priame pripojenie k serverom Google. Typy p\u00edsma, ktor\u00e9 si nain\u0161talujete, sa stiahnu zo slu\u017eby Google a ulo\u017eia sa na va\u0161u str\u00e1nku. Va\u0161a str\u00e1nka potom pou\u017eije tieto lok\u00e1lne hostovan\u00e9 typy p\u00edsma."],"Choose font variants. Keep in mind that too many variants could make your site slower.":["Vyberte si typy p\u00edsma. Majte na pam\u00e4ti, \u017ee pr\u00edli\u0161 ve\u013ea typov p\u00edsma m\u00f4\u017ee spomali\u0165 va\u0161u webov\u00fa str\u00e1nku."],"Font family uninstalled successfully.":["Rodina p\u00edsma bola \u00faspe\u0161ne odin\u0161talovan\u00e1."],"You can alternatively upload files directly on the Upload tab.":["Alternat\u00edvne m\u00f4\u017eete nahra\u0165 s\u00fabory priamo na karte Nahra\u0165."],"No fonts found. Try with a different search term.":["Nena\u0161li sa \u017eiadne typy p\u00edsma. Sk\u00faste pou\u017ei\u0165 in\u00fd v\u00fdraz."],"%1$d\/%2$d variants active":["%1$d\/%2$d variant akt\u00edvnych"],"Manage the fonts and typography used on captions.":["Spravujte fonty a typografiu pou\u017eit\u00fa na titulkoch."],"Manage the fonts and typography used on buttons.":["Spravujte p\u00edsma a typografiu pou\u017eit\u00fa na tla\u010didl\u00e1ch."],"Manage the fonts and typography used on headings.":["Spravujte p\u00edsma a typografiu pou\u017eit\u00fa na nadpisoch."],"font weight\u0004Black":["\u010cierna"],"font weight\u0004Bold":["Tu\u010dn\u00e9"],"font weight\u0004Medium":["Stredn\u00e9"],"font weight\u0004Thin":["Tenk\u00e9"],"font style\u0004Italic":["Kurz\u00edva"],"font weight\u0004Light":["Light"],"Rename":["Premenuj"],"Manage the fonts used on the site.":["Spravujte p\u00edsma pou\u017e\u00edvan\u00e9 na web str\u00e1nke."],"Manage the fonts and typography used on the links.":["Spravujte p\u00edsma a typografiu pou\u017eit\u00fa pre odkazy."],"Sorry, you are not allowed to upload this file type.":["Nem\u00e1te opr\u00e1vnenie nahra\u0165 s\u00fabor tohto typu."],"Captions":["Popisky"],"Buttons":["Tla\u010didl\u00e1"],"Headings":["Nadpisy"],"%d result found.":["N\u00e1jden\u00fd %d v\u00fdsledok.","N\u00e1jden\u00e9 %d vysledky.","N\u00e1jden\u00fdch %d v\u00fdsledkov."],"Category":["Kateg\u00f3ria"],"Reset":["Resetova\u0165"],"No blocks found.":["\u017diadny blok sa nena\u0161iel."],"Back":["Sp\u00e4\u0165"],"Upload":["Nahra\u0165"],"Text":["Text"],"Select all":["Vybra\u0165 v\u0161etko"],"Next page":["Nasleduj\u00faca strana"],"Previous page":["Predch\u00e1dzaj\u00faca strana"],"Default":["Predvolen\u00fd"],"Delete":["Zmaza\u0165"],"Install":["Nain\u0161talova\u0165"],"Cancel":["Zru\u0161i\